{"title":"线性代数（3）-- 矩阵乘法","uid":"9b44d47a13241d8ce0e5a630d2b9760b","slug":"线性代数（3）-- 矩阵乘法","date":"2022-05-02T04:35:35.000Z","updated":"2022-06-30T12:28:34.949Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/线性代数（3）-- 矩阵乘法.json","keywords":null,"cover":[],"content":"<h1 id=\"矩阵乘法和逆\">矩阵乘法和逆</h1>\r\n<h2 id=\"矩阵乘法\">矩阵乘法</h2>\r\n<h3 id=\"意义\">意义</h3>\r\n<p>前面说过， <code>矩阵</code> 是 <code>线性变换</code> 的记录法，那么\r\n<code>矩阵乘法</code> 就是几个 <code>线性变换</code> 的\r\n<strong>连续作用</strong></p>\r\n<h3 id=\"特例\">特例</h3>\r\n<ol type=\"1\">\r\n<li>剪切</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p><span class=\"math display\">\\[\r\n\\begin{bmatrix}\r\n1 &amp; 0\\\\\r\n1 &amp; 1\\\\\r\n\\end{bmatrix}\r\n\\]</span></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://s1.328888.xyz/2022/05/01/An0oX.jpg\" alt=\"Cut\" style=\"zoom:25%;\" /></p>\r\n<ol start=\"2\" type=\"1\">\r\n<li>旋转</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p><span class=\"math display\">\\[\r\n\\begin{bmatrix}\r\n-1 &amp; 0\\\\\r\n0 &amp; 1\\\\\r\n\\end{bmatrix}\r\n\\]</span></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://s1.328888.xyz/2022/05/01/Anpm7.jpg\" alt=\"Rot\" style=\"zoom:25%;\" /></p>\r\n<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(_{以RT∠为例}\\)</span></p>\r\n<h3 id=\"计算\">计算</h3>\r\n<code>线性变换</code> 需要记录 <code>基向量</code> 的位置，这时可以将\r\n<strong>右矩阵</strong> <em>按照列</em>\r\n<strong>分裂为多个基向量</strong> ，与 <strong>左矩阵</strong>\r\n分别相乘，得到新的 <code>基</code> ，再 <strong>合并回矩阵</strong>\r\n<span class=\"math inline\">\\(_{所得的结果也叫做复合变换}\\)</span><br />\r\n$$<br />\r\nAB=C\\<br />\r\n法(1):\\<br />\r\n\\<br />\r\n第三行<br />\r\n\r\n<span class=\"math display\">\\[\\begin{bmatrix}\r\n&amp; &amp; &amp; &amp;\\\\\r\n&amp; &amp; &amp; &amp;\\\\\r\n\\hline\\\\\r\n&amp; &amp; &amp; &amp;\\\\\r\n\\end{bmatrix}\\]</span>\r\n=<br />\r\n\r\n<span class=\"math display\">\\[\\begin{bmatrix}\r\n&amp; &amp; &amp; &amp; \\\\\r\n&amp; &amp; &amp; &amp; \\\\\r\n&amp; &amp; &amp; a_{34} &amp; \\\\\r\n&amp; &amp; &amp; &amp; \\\\\r\n\\end{bmatrix}\\]</span>\r\n<p>\\<br />\r\na_{34} = A的第三行 · B的第四列=^n_{k=1} a_{3k}b_{k4}\\</p>\r\n(2):\\<br />\r\n\r\n<span class=\"math display\">\\[\\begin{bmatrix}\r\n&amp; &amp; &amp; &amp; \\\\\r\n&amp; &amp; &amp; &amp; \\\\\r\n&amp; &amp; &amp; &amp; \\\\\r\n&amp; &amp; &amp; &amp; \\\\\r\n\\end{bmatrix}\\]</span>\r\n<p>=<br />\r\n\\<br />\r\nC的第一列=A·B的第一列\\<br />\r\n\\</p>\r\n(3):\\<br />\r\n\r\n<span class=\"math display\">\\[\\begin{bmatrix}\r\n&amp; &amp; &amp; &amp;\\\\\r\n&amp; &amp; &amp; &amp;\\\\\r\n\\hline\\\\\r\n&amp; &amp; &amp; &amp;\\\\\r\n\\end{bmatrix}\r\n\\begin{bmatrix}\r\n&amp; &amp; &amp; &amp; \\\\\r\n&amp; &amp; &amp; &amp; \\\\\r\n&amp; &amp; &amp; &amp; \\\\\r\n&amp; &amp; &amp; &amp; \\\\\r\n\\end{bmatrix}\\]</span>\r\n=<br />\r\n\r\n<span class=\"math display\">\\[\\begin{bmatrix}\r\n&amp; &amp; &amp; &amp;\\\\\r\n&amp; &amp; &amp; &amp;\\\\\r\n\\hline\\\\\r\n&amp; &amp; &amp; &amp;\\\\\r\n\\end{bmatrix}\\]</span>\r\n<p>\\<br />\r\nC的第三行=A的第三行·B\\<br />\r\n\\</p>\r\n(4):\\<br />\r\n\r\n<span class=\"math display\">\\[\\begin{bmatrix}\r\n&amp; &amp; &amp; &amp;\\\\\r\n&amp; &amp; &amp; &amp;\\\\\r\n\\hline\\\\\r\n&amp; &amp; &amp; &amp;\\\\\r\n\\end{bmatrix}\\]</span>\r\n<p>\\<br />\r\nC=^n_{k=1}A的第k行·B的第k列<br />\r\n$$</p>\r\n<h3 id=\"性质\">性质</h3>\r\n<ol type=\"1\">\r\n<li><strong>不满足交换律</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>先 <em>旋转</em> ，再 <em>剪切</em> ：</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://s1.328888.xyz/2022/05/01/AnI7C.jpg\" alt=\"img\" style=\"zoom:33%;\" /></p>\r\n<p>先 <em>剪切</em> ，再 <em>旋转</em> ：</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://s1.328888.xyz/2022/05/01/AnRjg.jpg\" alt=\"img\" style=\"zoom:33%;\" /></p>\r\n<p>可以发现，两个结果不同</p>\r\n<ol start=\"2\" type=\"1\">\r\n<li><p><strong>顺序要从右往左</strong></p></li>\r\n<li><p><strong>满足结合律</strong></p>\r\n<p><code>(AB)C</code> 可以看作 使用 <code>C</code> -&gt;使用\r\n<code>B</code> -&gt;使用<code>A</code></p>\r\n<p>而 <code>A(BC)</code> 也可看作 <code>C</code> -&gt; <code>B</code>\r\n-&gt; <code>A</code></p>\r\n<p>这两个 <strong>完全相同</strong> 啊！</p></li>\r\n<li><p><strong>左行右列</strong></p></li>\r\n<li><p><strong>矩阵的大小有严格规定</strong></p>\r\n<p><em>左矩阵列数</em> 与 <em>右矩阵行数</em> 相同</p>\r\n<p>所得的积 <em>行数</em> 为 <strong>左矩阵行数</strong>，<em>列数</em>\r\n为 <strong>右矩阵列数</strong></p>\r\n<p>用代数表述如下图：</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://s1.328888.xyz/2022/05/02/AjcWS.jpg\"\r\nalt=\"AjcWS.jpg\" /></p></li>\r\n<li><p><strong>可以分块计算，再重新合并</strong></p></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<h2 id=\"单位矩阵\">单位矩阵</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><p>单位矩阵：它满足 <span class=\"math inline\">\\(IM = M\\)</span></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://s1.328888.xyz/2022/05/18/DYcvi.jpg\" alt=\"DYcvi.jpg\" style=\"zoom:25%;\" /></p></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2 id=\"逆\">逆</h2>\r\n<p>逆存在： <span class=\"math inline\">\\(A^{-1}A = I\\)</span></p>\r\n<p>逆不存在：能找到 <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\mathbf{A\\vec x =\r\n0}(\\vec x \\ne 0)\\)</span> ，也就是 <strong>行列式为0</strong></p>\r\n<p><span class=\"math display\">\\[\r\n证:\\\\\r\n假设A存在逆:\\\\\r\n\\because A\\vec x = 0 (\\vec x \\ne 0)\\\\\r\n\\therefore A^{-1}A\\vec x = 0 A^{-1}0\\\\\r\n\\therefore A^{-1}A\\vec x = 0\\\\\r\n又\\because A^{-1}A = I\\\\\r\n\\therefore I\\vec x = 0\\\\\r\n\\therefore \\vec x = 0\\\\\r\n又\\because  \\vec x \\ne 0\\\\\r\n\\therefore A不存在逆\r\n\\]</span></p>\r\n<p>求逆：</p>\r\n$$<br />\r\n对\r\n<span class=\"math display\">\\[\\begin{bmatrix}\r\n1 &amp; 3\\\\\r\n2 &amp; 7\\\\\r\n\\end{bmatrix}\\]</span>\r\n求逆\\\\<br />\r\n解:\\<br />\r\n设:<br />\r\n\r\n<span class=\"math display\">\\[\\begin{bmatrix}\r\n1 &amp; 3\\\\\r\n2 &amp; 7\\\\\r\n\\end{bmatrix}\r\n\\begin{bmatrix}\r\na &amp; c\\\\\r\nb &amp; d\\\\\r\n\\end{bmatrix}\\]</span>\r\n<p>=I\\<br />\r\n 对<br />\r\n进行消元\\</p>\r\n<p>=<br />\r\n(完成高斯消元)\\</p>\r\n<p>=<br />\r\n\\</p>\r\n<h1 id=\"-1\">^{-1}</h1>\r\n<span class=\"math display\">\\[\\begin{bmatrix}\r\n7 &amp; -3\\\\\r\n-2 &amp; 1\\\\\r\n\\end{bmatrix}\\]</span>\r\n\\<br />\r\n\\<br />\r\n检:\\<br />\r\n\r\n<span class=\"math display\">\\[\\begin{bmatrix}\r\n7 &amp; -3\\\\\r\n-2 &amp; 1\\\\\r\n\\end{bmatrix}\r\n\\begin{bmatrix}\r\n1 &amp; 3\\\\\r\n2 &amp; 7\\\\\r\n\\end{bmatrix}\\]</span>\r\n=<br />\r\n\r\n<span class=\"math display\">\\[\\begin{bmatrix}\r\n7\\times 1-3\\times 2 &amp; 7\\times 3 -3\\times 7\\\\\r\n-2\\times 1 +1\\times 2 &amp; -2\\times 3 + 1\\times 7\\\\\r\n\\end{bmatrix}\\]</span>\r\n<h1 id=\"section\">\\</h1>\r\n<span class=\"math display\">\\[\\begin{bmatrix}\r\n1 &amp; 0\\\\\r\n0 &amp; 1\\\\\r\n\\end{bmatrix}\\]</span>\r\n\\<br />\r\n<br />\r\n\r\n<span class=\"math display\">\\[\\begin{bmatrix}\r\n1 &amp; 3\\\\\r\n2 &amp; 7\\\\\r\n\\end{bmatrix}\\]</span>\r\n<h1 id=\"-1-1\">^{-1}</h1>\r\n<span class=\"math display\">\\[\\begin{bmatrix}\r\n7 &amp; -3\\\\\r\n-2 &amp; 1\\\\\r\n\\end{bmatrix}\\]</span>\r\n<p>检毕<br />\r\n$$</p>\r\n<p>证：高斯-诺尔当消元求逆</p>\r\n<p><span class=\"math display\">\\[\r\nE[A|I]=AE + EI(矩阵分块乘法)\\\\\r\n又\\because AE=I\\\\\r\n\\therefore E[A|I]=I+E\\\\\r\n\\therefore E[A|I]=[I|E]\\\\\r\n又\\because AE=I\\\\\r\n\\therefore A^{-1}=E\r\n\\therefore E[A|I]=[I|A^{-1}]\\\\\r\n\\]</span></p>\r\n<p>证毕。</p>\r\n<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(E.g:\\)</span></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://s1.328888.xyz/2022/05/18/DYGqy.jpg\" alt=\"DYGqy.jpg\" style=\"zoom:30%;\" /><img src=\"https://s1.328888.xyz/2022/05/18/DYyUW.jpg\" alt=\"DYyUW.jpg\" style=\"zoom:31%;\" /></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://s1.328888.xyz/2022/05/18/DY9od.jpg\" alt=\"DY9od.jpg\" style=\"zoom:35%;\" /><img src=\"https://s1.328888.xyz/2022/05/18/DYL2Q.jpg\" alt=\"DYL2Q.jpg\" style=\"zoom:31%;\" /></p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p><strong>下课！</strong></p>\r\n","text":"矩阵乘法和逆 矩阵乘法 意义 前面说过， 矩阵 是 线性变换 的记录法，那么 矩阵乘法 就是几个 线性变换 的 连续作用 特例 剪切 \\[ \\begin{bmatrix} 1 &amp; 0\\\\ 1 &amp; 1\\\\ \\end{bmatrix} \\] 旋转 \\[ \\begin{...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"3.1k","symbolsTime":"3 mins."},"categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"Math","slug":"Math","count":5,"path":"api/tags/Math.json"},{"name":"Linear-Algebra","slug":"Linear-Algebra","count":5,"path":"api/tags/Linear-Algebra.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%9F%A9%E9%98%B5%E4%B9%98%E6%B3%95%E5%92%8C%E9%80%86\"><span class=\"toc-text\">矩阵乘法和逆</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%9F%A9%E9%98%B5%E4%B9%98%E6%B3%95\"><span class=\"toc-text\">矩阵乘法</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%84%8F%E4%B9%89\"><span class=\"toc-text\">意义</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%89%B9%E4%BE%8B\"><span class=\"toc-text\">特例</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97\"><span class=\"toc-text\">计算</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%80%A7%E8%B4%A8\"><span class=\"toc-text\">性质</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%8D%95%E4%BD%8D%E7%9F%A9%E9%98%B5\"><span class=\"toc-text\">单位矩阵</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E9%80%86\"><span class=\"toc-text\">逆</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#-1\"><span class=\"toc-text\">^{-1}</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#section\"><span class=\"toc-text\">\\</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#-1-1\"><span class=\"toc-text\">^{-1}</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"YingHN","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210313122054101.png","link":"/","description":"","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{"title":"中国历史（1）-- 隋唐时期","uid":"2fa21c74fe45e7f6717ebf3ebc54e97b","slug":"中国历史（1）-- 隋唐时期","date":"2022-05-03T08:48:56.000Z","updated":"2022-05-03T08:52:22.020Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/中国历史（1）-- 隋唐时期.json","keywords":null,"cover":[],"text":"中国历史（1）-- 隋唐时期 时代特征：繁荣与开放 隋 建立 时间： AD581 建立者：隋文帝杨